      "movement_state": "Walk",
      "dialog_text": "Lisa, we need to hide now. Let's go behind the cafe bar counter.",
      "plan": "That gunshot was terrifying—this is no time for art talk. I need to find a safe place to hide, somewhere close and out of sight.",
